### What problem does this feature solve?
It is useful to pass style information into component instance in runtime. There is a computed style attribute approach, but the code using that way is not really clean while style information could be really big.

### What does the proposed API look like?
```
<template>

    <div>{{ display }}</div>

</template>


<script>

    export default {
        data(){
            return { display: 'block' }
        }
    }

</script>


<style>
    body {
        display: {{ display }}
    }
</style>
```

